| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4493 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5f3e51b9-2e5e-5f9d-bdd4-a2928ed846cd"
